&lt;p&gt;This offer is currently exclusive to LET, stock is limited.
Here is the link to the plan: &lt;a href="https://www.fitvps.com/members/cart.php?a=add&amp;amp;pid=19" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"&gt;https://www.fitvps.com/members/cart.php?a=add&amp;amp;pid=19&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There is also a promotion included - &lt;b&gt;order with 2GB RAM, get upgraded to 4GB RAM for free&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To get this server You should not order directly on the website, instead you PM me if you are interested
